About Me:
I'm just starting my journey in the car-sharing industry, and I couldn't be more excited to share my passion for cars with you. My goal is to provide a seamless and memorable experience for every renter, making sure you enjoy every moment behind the wheel of this stunning vehicle.
My Vehicle:
2022 Chevrolet Corvette: This high-performance sports car is wrapped in a striking burnt red color, guaranteed to turn heads wherever you go. With its powerful V8 engine and luxurious interior, the Corvette offers both thrilling performance and unparalleled comfort.
Why Choose My Corvette?
Exceptional Performance: Experience the thrill of driving one of the most iconic sports cars. The Corvette's powerful engine and advanced features ensure an exhilarating ride.
Luxurious Comfort: Step inside and enjoy the premium leather seats, advanced technology, and high-quality materials that make every drive a pleasure.
Meticulous Maintenance: I take great pride in keeping my Corvette in pristine condition. Regular servicing and meticulous cleaning ensure that the car is always ready for your next adventure.
Convenience and Flexibility:
I understand that your travel plans can change, so I offer flexible rental options to fit your needs. Whether you’re looking for a short-term rental for a special occasion or an extended trip, I’ve got you covered. The pickup location at 1030 Western Ave, Glendale, California, makes it easy for you to start your journey without any hassle.
Exceptional Customer Service:
Your satisfaction is my top priority. I’m always available to assist with any questions or concerns you may have, ensuring a smooth and enjoyable rental experience. I aim to exceed your expectations and make your rental experience as pleasant as possible.
Safety and Peace of Mind:
Your safety is my utmost concern. The Corvette is insured and undergoes regular maintenance checks to ensure it’s in optimal condition. You can drive with confidence knowing that you're in a well-maintained and safe vehicle.
Positive Reviews:
I’m dedicated to providing an outstanding rental experience, and I look forward to receiving your positive feedback. Your satisfaction and enjoyment are my greatest rewards.
Book with me today and experience the thrill, luxury, and exceptional service that come with renting my 2022 Chevrolet Corvette. I’m excited to be your trusted partner for all your car rental needs and look forward to making your next drive an unforgettable adventure.

Hi I’m Taylor! I graduated from USC on a full ride scholarship and studied real estate development. I am renting out my Range Rover because I just bought a 2nd car for fun. I am trying to make additional income to help offset my car expenses. My favorite cars are Range Rover, Porsche, and Ferrari. 

I grew up in Newport Beach (Orange County) and I have been living in LA for 6 years. I know California well, and can recommend the best restaurants, beaches, hiking trails, scenic drives, and everything in between! I am trying to focus on working with repeat, trustworthy renters. 

Also, I work for one of the top real estate developers and we are building industrial and multifamily in CO and AZ now. If you are interested in OZ projects or real estate investing, please let me know. We have about 480 investors currently and an average annual net to investor return of 25% since 1995.
